00:20:57,930 --> 00:21:01,220
Tak kuat sangat. Pakai gelang je dah buat dia tak nampak.

259
00:21:01,570 --> 00:21:03,720
Roh macam ni tak rumit.

260
00:21:13,310 --> 00:21:14,140
Thit.

261
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:15,540
Thit.

262
00:21:18,980 --> 00:21:19,900
Arthit.

263
00:21:20,360 --> 00:21:24,510
Thit, Thit, Thit, Thit.

264
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:27,090
Thit.

265
00:21:33,670 --> 00:21:35,110
Thit, Thit, Thit.

266
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:25,320
Kau lambat lagi.

267
00:22:27,260 --> 00:22:28,630
Kau pun baru sampai, sial.

268
00:22:44,810 --> 00:22:45,680
Hei.

269
00:23:00,450 --> 00:23:01,230
Korang lambat.

270
00:23:01,560 --> 00:23:02,480
Aku dah cuba.

271
00:23:03,610 --> 00:23:04,630
Jo yang lambat.

272
00:23:44,060 --> 00:23:46,670
Jadi, kamu dah pindah ke bilik baru?

273
00:23:46,850 --> 00:23:47,870
Ya, Papa.

274
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:51,100
Bila kamu nak bawa Mr. John datang?

275
00:23:51,830 --> 00:23:54,320
Em, saya tak lapang sekarang.

276
00:23:54,560 --> 00:23:55,860
Boleh minggu depan?

277
00:23:58,260 --> 00:23:59,060
Boleh.

278
00:23:59,420 --> 00:24:02,070
Dan bilik baru tu—tak ada apa-apa pelik, kan?

279
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:04,050
Papa tengok sewa dia murah.

280
00:24:04,630 --> 00:24:06,360
Jadi Papa risau sikit.

281
00:24:07,040 --> 00:24:09,340
Jangan fikir sangat, Papa.

282
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:11,480
Biar saya cakap dengan Dad.

283
00:24:12,490 --> 00:24:13,210
Ya, ya.

284
00:24:13,410 --> 00:24:15,030
Hei, anak kamu nak cakap dengan kamu.

285
00:24:15,140 --> 00:24:15,770
Okey.

286
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:20,270
Hei, nak. Bila kamu balik rumah?

287
00:24:21,250 --> 00:24:22,260
Saya baru sampai.

288
00:24:22,770 --> 00:24:25,150
Boleh ambil gambar Mr. John untuk saya?

289
00:24:26,020 --> 00:24:27,450
Boleh, nanti saya hantar pada Dad.

290
00:24:27,980 --> 00:24:28,930
Macam mana bilik kamu?

291
00:24:30,630 --> 00:24:33,330
Luas sangat dan senang.

292
00:24:33,630 --> 00:24:34,590
Baguslah.

293
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:35,840
Jumpa nanti.

294
00:24:36,190 --> 00:24:37,000
Jumpa lagi.

295
00:24:57,420 --> 00:24:58,900
Cukup tak untuk kenyang?

296
00:25:00,850 --> 00:25:02,300
Aku tak berapa lapar.

297
00:25:02,770 --> 00:25:05,460
Degilnya kau, Michael. Nanti aku beritahu Ter.

298
00:25:06,550 --> 00:25:07,580
Jangan.

299
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:10,520
Kau gelak apa?

300
00:25:11,310 --> 00:25:17,580
Kalau Ter, North, Phoon, Michael mesti mengalah.

301
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:19,040
Mm.

302
00:25:20,390 --> 00:25:22,670
Mereka kawan aku.

303
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:48,920
Sakitlah.

304
00:26:49,320 --> 00:26:52,090
Aku marah kalau kau asyik buat aku sakit macam tu.

305
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:56,220
Hulur tangan, aku nak pukul.

306
00:27:00,010 --> 00:27:03,670
Sakit. Jangan buat aku macam tu.

307
00:27:05,830 --> 00:27:08,150
Aku tak boleh bernafas.

308
00:27:08,750 --> 00:27:11,200
- Aku takkan buat.
- Sakit.

309
00:27:19,660 --> 00:27:20,620
Tumpang tanya.

310
00:27:38,995 --> 00:27:40,260
Ada apa-apa tak kena?

311
00:27:42,310 --> 00:27:42,980
Tak.

312
00:27:47,260 --> 00:27:49,290
Nasib baik pintu tertutup.

313
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:29,730
Kau buat apa?

314
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:35,840
Tak bercakap.

315
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:38,820
Aku nak tidur.

316
00:28:44,540 --> 00:28:45,860
Kalau ada nak cakap, cakaplah.

317
00:28:46,610 --> 00:28:47,640
Nama kau Dao, kan?

318
00:28:48,020 --> 00:28:48,670
Ya.

319
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:51,300
Aku nak minta tolong kau pasal sesuatu.

320
00:28:52,540 --> 00:28:53,430
Tolong pasal apa?

321
00:28:59,780 --> 00:29:00,990
Aku nak Pad Kra Pao Mak Cik Jum.

322
00:29:07,530 --> 00:29:10,540
Tolonglah. Aku teringin nak makan.

323
00:29:11,470 --> 00:29:12,830
Kau tarik kaki aku—

324
00:29:13,530 --> 00:29:15,790
—semata-mata nak Pad Kra Pao Mak Cik Jum?

325
00:29:16,470 --> 00:29:17,100
Bukan.

326
00:29:18,620 --> 00:29:19,380
Ada benda lain.

327
00:29:26,790 --> 00:29:27,650
Apa dia?

328
00:29:29,850 --> 00:29:30,980
Tolong aku cari tahu

329
00:29:31,850 --> 00:29:32,882
siapa yang bunuh aku.

330
00:29:33,700 --> 00:29:35,080
Bukan teman wanita kau ke?

331
00:29:35,220 --> 00:29:36,710
Yang bunuh kau tu?

332
00:29:36,810 --> 00:29:38,220
Aku tak percaya teman wanita aku buat.

333
00:29:40,710 --> 00:29:43,140
Tolong. Aku merayu.

334
00:29:44,140 --> 00:29:45,060
Tak.

335
00:29:45,469 --> 00:29:46,400
Aku tak nak terlibat.

336
00:29:47,810 --> 00:29:49,240
Kenapa kau kejam sangat?

337
00:29:49,450 --> 00:29:51,130
Luaran kau nampak baik sangat.

338
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,310
Tak boleh tolong aku ke?

339
00:29:57,740 --> 00:29:59,360
Tolonglah, bantu aku.

340
00:29:59,610 --> 00:30:00,400
Tolong?

341
00:30:03,230 --> 00:30:04,980
Kalau tak, aku kacau kau tiap malam macam ni.

342
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:06,560
Kau tahu tempat kau tidur tu—

343
00:30:07,660 --> 00:30:08,630
—itulah tempat aku mati.

344
00:30:10,376 --> 00:30:11,590
Aku boleh buat apa saja pada kau.

345
00:30:12,770 --> 00:30:13,670
Kau ugut aku?

346
00:30:26,110 --> 00:30:27,440
Jadi macam mana kau nak aku tolong?

347
00:30:30,460 --> 00:30:31,040
Aku tak tahu.

348
00:30:32,010 --> 00:30:32,540
Apa?

349
00:30:33,620 --> 00:30:35,310
Cuba tanya pelajar perubatan sebelah.

350
00:30:35,710 --> 00:30:36,860
Dia kenal teman wanita aku.

351
00:30:53,970 --> 00:30:55,720
Hei, kau dah habis kelas?

352
00:30:56,360 --> 00:30:57,730
Hari ni aku tak ada kelas.

353
00:30:59,500 --> 00:31:00,240
Jadi kau buat apa?

354
00:31:00,770 --> 00:31:01,570
Tidur.

355
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:05,130
Tidur petang? Nanti hantu tindih.

356
00:31:07,390 --> 00:31:08,300
Ada apa?

357
00:31:09,777 --> 00:31:11,880
Aku baru habis kelas. Aku datang jumpa kau.

358
00:31:12,330 --> 00:31:13,490
Kenapa?

359
00:31:14,613 --> 00:31:15,911
Okey, jumpa nanti.

360
00:31:49,760 --> 00:31:50,940
Kau betul-betul boleh duduk sini?

361
00:31:53,080 --> 00:31:54,090
Ya, boleh.

362
00:31:57,582 --> 00:31:59,994
Aku dengar tempat ni ada…

363
00:32:03,750 --> 00:32:04,890
ada…

364
00:32:07,190 --> 00:32:10,130
sejarah yang agak teruk.

365
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:14,470
Mungkin tak selamat untuk kau.

366
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:24,770
Semua orang cuma risau pasal kau.

367
00:32:25,010 --> 00:32:26,540
Ter dengan Phoon pun risau.

368
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:28,460
North macam mana?

369
00:32:29,430 --> 00:32:30,510
Aku?

370
00:32:30,910 --> 00:32:32,140
Kenapa aku nak risau pasal kau?

371
00:32:35,660 --> 00:32:37,290
Kau tak payah risau pasal aku.

372
00:32:37,660 --> 00:32:40,510
Bila pemilik kondominium tahu apa jadi sini,

373
00:32:40,890 --> 00:32:43,420
dia ketatkan kawalan keselamatan.

374
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:44,930
Sewa pun murah.

375
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:46,480
Lagipun,

376
00:32:46,750 --> 00:32:47,890
tak ramai orang.

377
00:32:48,110 --> 00:32:49,310
Memang macam aku suka.

378
00:32:51,500 --> 00:32:55,340
Mm. Kalau kau boleh terima, terpulang pada kau.

379
00:32:58,810 --> 00:33:00,540
Kau tak jumpa benda pelik, kan?

380
00:33:02,850 --> 00:33:06,600
Lebih 20 minit lagi P’Jo ambil aku. Nak main game?

381
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:08,420
Ya, boleh.

382
00:33:32,750 --> 00:33:34,530
Sejujurnya, Dao,

383
00:33:34,820 --> 00:33:38,420
Aku nampak kau nak hantar aku depan, jadi aku ikut.

384
00:33:38,630 --> 00:33:39,690
Sebenarnya,

385
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:41,950
- Aku boleh balik sendiri.
- Hei.

386
00:33:42,970 --> 00:33:43,980
Oh, P’Thit.

387
00:33:45,010 --> 00:33:45,720
Kau buat apa di sini?

388
00:33:46,270 --> 00:33:46,840
Err,

389
00:33:47,490 --> 00:33:49,610
kawan aku tinggal sini, jadi aku datang jumpa dia.

390
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:54,290
Kau pula? Kau buat apa di sini?

391
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:55,650
Kau tinggal sini?

392
00:33:57,050 --> 00:33:57,650
Ya.

393
00:33:58,190 --> 00:33:59,150
Bilik mana?

394
00:34:03,570 --> 00:34:04,260
Sebelah?

395
00:34:04,710 --> 00:34:05,280
Mm.

396
00:34:06,500 --> 00:34:07,990
Sial, kebetulan betul.

397
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:13,030
Legalah. Tinggal dia sorang memang seram gila.

398
00:34:14,190 --> 00:34:14,630
Hei.

399
00:34:15,870 --> 00:34:18,860
Atau kau sebelah lagi menakutkan?

400
00:34:21,390 --> 00:34:24,280
Hei, P’Thit.
Kau turunkan aku sini je.

401
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:26,570
Jumpa lagi. P’Thit, bagi aku tengok bilik kau.

402
00:34:27,470 --> 00:34:28,970
Kenapa kau ikut aku, North?

403
00:34:29,090 --> 00:34:30,960
- Bagi aku masuk.
- Tak perlu.

404
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:34,830
Tak masuk akal.

405
00:34:35,560 --> 00:34:36,660
Kenapa kau masuk?

406
00:34:39,690 --> 00:34:40,590
Tanggalkan kasut juga.

407
00:34:43,640 --> 00:34:44,690
Sial.

408
00:34:47,830 --> 00:34:49,180
Baik gila.

409
00:34:54,810 --> 00:34:55,460
Hei.

410
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:58,070
Cantiknya, P'!

411
00:34:58,500 --> 00:34:59,370
Berapa harganya?

412
00:34:59,690 --> 00:35:01,890
Dalam dua tiga ratus ribu kot. Tak ingat.

413
00:35:02,060 --> 00:35:02,900
Dia gigit tak?

414
00:35:03,410 --> 00:35:04,690
- Nak cuba?
- Tak payah.

415
00:35:04,890 --> 00:35:05,960
Jangan buka. Jangan.

416
00:35:10,180 --> 00:35:13,470
Kau kata dulu kau sorang satu tingkat ni, kan?

417
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:14,670
Betul ke?

418
00:35:15,770 --> 00:35:16,510
Ya.

419
00:35:17,230 --> 00:35:18,540
Sekarang kawan kau dah ada sini.

420
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:23,510
Kawan saya dah pindah masuk, tolong jaga dia.

421
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:24,890
Kenapa dia pindah sini?

422
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:27,420
Ingatkan aku boleh duduk sorang sampai grad.

423
00:35:27,790 --> 00:35:30,180
Tuan rumah bagi bilik tu diskaun 70%.

424
00:35:30,270 --> 00:35:32,220
Hah? 70%?

425
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:34,880
Ya, sebab tu dia terus pindah masuk.

426
00:35:35,750 --> 00:35:37,350
Aku cuma dapat 50%, sial.

427
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:40,510
Itu lagi banyak dari aku.

428
00:35:41,330 --> 00:35:41,740
Err...

429
00:35:43,050 --> 00:35:43,630
Kenapa dengan kau?

430
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:46,650
Ada orang mati dalam bilik tu.

431
00:35:46,830 --> 00:35:49,160
Kalau nak diskaun lagi besar, kau pindah sana.

432
00:35:49,220 --> 00:35:51,170
Tak nak!

433
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:53,240
Suka hati kau.

434
00:35:54,730 --> 00:35:55,890
Apa hal kau ni?

435
00:35:56,140 --> 00:35:57,030
Sebelah je.

436
00:36:00,810 --> 00:36:02,410
Dah, boleh balik sekarang?

437
00:36:02,940 --> 00:36:04,880
Aku penat. Aku nak tidur.

438
00:36:05,040 --> 00:36:06,100
Kenapa halau aku?

439
00:36:06,670 --> 00:36:07,440
Okey, aku pergi.

440
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:08,580
Sial.

441
00:36:09,690 --> 00:36:11,140
P'Jo dah sampai belum?

442
00:36:11,930 --> 00:36:14,020
Sepatutnya dah. Dia keluar sekali dengan aku.

443
00:36:15,970 --> 00:36:16,470
Mm.

444
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:18,300
Jom.

445
00:36:20,520 --> 00:36:22,330
- Teman aku turun bawah.
- Hah?

446
00:36:23,590 --> 00:36:25,630
Sial, North. Kau dah besar panjang.

447
00:36:25,970 --> 00:36:28,660
Kau dah tinggi macam kerbau. Dah, keluar.

448
00:36:29,410 --> 00:36:30,450
Tolonglah, P'.

449
00:36:30,500 --> 00:36:31,530
Teman aku turun.

450
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:32,730
Tolong.

451
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:37,690
North nampak comel pakai uniform jurutera hari ni.

452
00:36:38,780 --> 00:36:40,840
Hari-hari kau kata dia comel.

453
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:43,290
Dia rapat dengan jiran sebelah tu?

454
00:36:44,890 --> 00:36:46,630
Dia kawan teman lelaki North.

455
00:36:47,260 --> 00:36:50,090
Teman lelaki North hensem. Diorang serasi.

456
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:52,260
Mm.

457
00:36:58,060 --> 00:36:58,850
Kenapa dengan kau?

458
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:04,250
Lambatnya. Tak boleh ikut aku ke?

459
00:37:05,270 --> 00:37:05,970
Diamlah.

460
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:15,870
Okey, jumpa lagi.

461
00:37:16,380 --> 00:37:17,290
Jumpa lagi.

462
00:37:44,610 --> 00:37:45,710
Apa hal?

463
00:37:46,570 --> 00:37:47,810
Ini ayah kau.

464
00:37:48,130 --> 00:37:49,180
Jaga mulut.

465
00:37:50,780 --> 00:37:51,570
Direk.

466
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:53,650
Aku ni kawan kau ke apa?

467
00:37:56,130 --> 00:37:57,310
Direk ayah aku.

468
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:02,520
Kalau nak jadi kawan, cakap je.

469
00:38:03,670 --> 00:38:06,680
Budak ni. Kalau kau bukan anak aku—

470
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:10,300
Jadi apa? Kenapa telefon?

471
00:38:10,430 --> 00:38:12,760
Hei, kau dah lama tak pergi litar lumba?

472
00:38:13,690 --> 00:38:15,700
Aku sibuk gila, Direk.

473
00:38:15,990 --> 00:38:19,500
Syif pagi malam tak henti. Aku nak berhenti, Direk.

474
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:21,280
Sokong aku, boleh?

475
00:38:22,290 --> 00:38:24,530
Apa, aku tak sokong kau lagi ke? Hah?

476
00:38:24,890 --> 00:38:27,530
Serius, mana nak cari ayah hebat macam aku?

477
00:38:27,630 --> 00:38:28,570
Alah.

478
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:32,740
Dan jangan sekat aku kat LINE lagi.

479
00:38:33,620 --> 00:38:34,730
Aku dah buka sekatan.

480
00:38:35,690 --> 00:38:37,580
Asyik suruh Johan cakap dengan aku.

481
00:38:37,740 --> 00:38:40,880
Ala, Direk. Kau elok je cakap dengan Jo.

482
00:38:41,370 --> 00:38:43,740
Tapi dengan anak sendiri, kau tak nak cakap.

483
00:38:44,020 --> 00:38:45,650
Johan comel.

484
00:38:45,810 --> 00:38:47,660
Dia cakap pun masuk akal.

485
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:48,260
Oh?

486
00:38:50,180 --> 00:38:51,690
Jadi aku tak masuk akal ke?

487
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:53,070
Kau menyampah.

488
00:38:53,190 --> 00:38:54,210
Apa masalah kau?

489
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:57,830
Kau telefon asyik minta duit. Ingat aku kaya?

490
00:38:58,010 --> 00:39:01,160
Kalau tak kaya, cakap je. Aku pinjam Jo.

491
00:39:04,190 --> 00:39:04,810
Jadi?

492
00:39:05,770 --> 00:39:06,460
Apa dia?

493
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:07,900
Kenapa telefon?

494
00:39:10,780 --> 00:39:11,780
Aku mimpi buruk.

495
00:39:12,040 --> 00:39:14,620
Sial, aku kena pujuk kau pula?

496
00:39:14,770 --> 00:39:15,820
Tak apa, Ayah.

497
00:39:15,930 --> 00:39:18,970
Mimpi buruk tu jadi benda baik, ya?
Macam tu?

498
00:39:19,120 --> 00:39:21,990
Ayah konon.

499
00:39:22,620 --> 00:39:23,470
Kau sumpah diri sendiri lagi.

500
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:30,200
Oh? Kau mimpi pasal apa?

501
00:39:31,970 --> 00:39:33,180
Aku mimpi pasal mak kau.

502
00:39:45,330 --> 00:39:46,130
Emma?

503
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:47,930
Ya.

504
00:39:54,860 --> 00:39:56,050
Dia cakap apa?

505
00:39:58,980 --> 00:40:00,360
Dia tak cakap apa-apa.

506
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:01,430
Macam biasa.

507
00:40:08,300 --> 00:40:10,190
Mungkin kau kerja kuat sangat, Direk.

508
00:40:10,780 --> 00:40:11,920
Rehatlah.

509
00:40:14,060 --> 00:40:15,420
Ya, mungkin.

510
00:40:22,720 --> 00:40:23,430
Mm.

511
00:41:03,850 --> 00:41:06,180
Esok aku nak tidur puas-puas. Cuti aku.

512
00:41:07,740 --> 00:41:10,310
